{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Report VAT fraud"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/report-vat-fraud.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/report-vat-fraud"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"2368","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Reporting VAT fraud to HM Revenue & Customs anonymously ","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:13:57+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You can report someone to HM Revenue &amp; Customs (<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>) if you think they\u2019re committing <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud - you don\u2019t have to give your name.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can report <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://online.hmrc.gov.uk/shortforms/form/CusConf_InformB?dept-name=Customs&amp;sub-dept-name=Hotline&amp;location=48&amp;origin=http://www.hmrc.gov.uk\" title=\"Customs Hotline\"><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud online</a> or by telephone. </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Customs 24 hour hotline</strong><br />\n0800 595 000</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>For your own safety don&rsquo;t:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>try to find out more about the fraud</li>\n  <li>let anyone know you&rsquo;re reporting it</li>\n  <li>encourage anyone to commit a crime so you can get more information</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>What is <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud?</h2>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud is when a business doesn&rsquo;t charge <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> when they should, or charges you <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> but doesn&rsquo;t pay it to <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>. For example, they might:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>ask you to pay cash to avoid paying <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> on a sale or job</li>\n  <li>not be registered for <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> when they should be</li>\n  <li>use a <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> number that&rsquo;s false or belongs to someone else</li>\n  <li>claim to have applied for a <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> number when they haven&rsquo;t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can <a href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/vies/vatRequest.html\" title=\"VIES VAT number validation\" rel=\"external\">check a UK <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> number is valid.</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"VAT","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/tax%2Fvat.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes returns online, rates, charging and record keeping","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fvat","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/vat"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Report 'cash in hand' pay","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/report-cash-in-hand-pay.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-cash-in-hand-pay","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2370","business_proposition":true}}]]],"parts":null}